  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para><list>
<item>Explain the meaning of &#8220;conservation of momentum&#8221;</item>
<item>Correctly identify if a system is, or is not, closed</item>
<item>Define a system whose momentum is conserved</item>
<item>Mathematically express conservation of momentum for a given system</item>
<item>Calculate an unknown quantity using conservation of momentum</item>
</list></md:abstract>
